worldattribute-yeet-SatietyCost: The amount of satiety lost when yeeting.
worldattribute-yeet-WooshVolume: Volume of the 'woosh' noise when an item is yeeted.
worldattribute-yeet-WooshAudibleRange: Furthest distance at which the 'woosh' noise can be heard.
worldattribute-yeet-GruntVolume: Volume of the player's grunting when yeeting.
worldattribute-yeet-GruntAudibleRange: Furthest distance at which the grunting of a yeeting player can be heard.
worldattribute-yeet-MaxShockwaveRingsToS: Maximum number of shockwave particle rings to spawn per yeeted item.
worldattribute-yeet-MinDelayBetweenRings: Minimum milliseconds to wait before spawning a shockwave particle ring.
worldattribute-yeet-MaxDelayBetweenRings: Maximum milliseconds to wait before spawning a shockwave particle ring.
worldattribute-yeet-ParticlesPerRing: Number of particles to spawn per shockwave.
worldattribute-yeet-ShockwaveVelocityFac: Velocity of the shockwave particles compared to the velocity of the yeeted item.
